  Description: LSTween is a powerful animation and tweening engine for Spectacles, based on the popular Tween.js library. It provides smooth property interpolation for transforms, colors, materials, and custom values with support for easing functions, chaining, repeating, and yo-yo effects. Perfect for creating...
